      "content": "it just feels like i'm performing a role for a person who doesn't exist anymore. like i'm just a hollow shell walking around pretending to be alive. if the person everyone cared about is gone, what's the point of keeping the body around? it feels so pointless to just keep existing when there's nobody actually home.",
